
# Switch statement #

Desired features:
 - Should support the standard equality-search
 - Could also support boolean checking, and possibly replace if_block
 - Should support type switching

Possible syntaxes:
 
 switch (value)
   case something: call(b)
   case somethingElse: call(c)
   default: ...

 switch (value)
   case(something) call(b)
   case(somethingElse) call(b); return a + b

 switch (value) 
   case something { b = something() }
